>>>>>>> Diabetes UK is supporting the NHS to improve local diabetes care by
involving people living with diabetes. Find out how 19 NHS organisations are
taking action to improve diabetes services in line with the needs of local
people, in the Improving Local Services Together project run by Diabetes UK
>>>>>>> ## NHS organisations – learning and resources for involving diabetes
>>>>>>> Go to the links below for each of theNHS organisationswe partnered to
see what was achieved including results of user focus groups, recommendations
>>>>>>> A report bringing together all the findings of the project which ended
in September 2014 will be published here in December 2014. It will evaluate
the intervention and the impact of the work with project partners, identify
good practice and will be useful for other NHS organisations seeking to
undertake patient involvement in the planning, design and delivery of local
